        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/fibreglass-pools/"><h3>Fibreglass pools</h3><p>$32K&ndash;$60K. Aqua-Tech, Compass, Leisure Pools shells. 3&ndash;5 week install.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/pool-resurfacing/"><h3>Pool resurfacing</h3><p>$9K&ndash;$60K. Pebble, quartz or full-tile re-interior. 7&ndash;14 day project.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/equipment-upgrades/"><h3>Equipment upgrades</h3><p>$1.5K&ndash;$9K. Variable-speed pump, chlorinator, heating, automation, LED.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/pool-renovation/"><h3>Pool renovation</h3><p>$8K&ndash;$80K. Coping, paving, surround, structural repair, glass fence integration.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
